    <%= @greeting %>,

    A client is seeking your services. Please review the below details about the request and reply to the client with a quotation.

    Client name: <%= "#{@client.first_name} #{@client.last_name}"%>
    Searching for: <%= @request.service %>
  	Location: <%= @request.location %>
    Description of work:
    <% @answers.each do |answer| %>
          <% if answer.answer.present?%>
            <%if answer.question.answer_type != "email_field"%>
              <%=answer.question.question%>
              <%=answer.answer%>
            <%end%>
          <%end%>
    <% end %>

	<%= link_to "Send a Quote", request_url(@request), class: "btn btn-primary btn-block" %>
